subtitleNullable: Reduced version of the CelebA dataset, for facial recognition practices
descriptionNullable:
This is a reduced version of the CelebA dataset. Basically, I reduced the number of celebrities present in the dataset to 1000, which resulted in 21,152 images, totaling around 150MB.

The original dataset can be found at: https://mmlab.ie.cuhk.edu.hk/projects/CelebA.html
